title=Local Requirements
1 No NIS accounts on public servers.
2 An idle screen soon locks itself.
3 Remote administration is configured (e.g., BigFix).
4 Syslog service runs automatically.
5 ntp.conf uses only trusted servers (NTPUserGuideV6.pdf).
6 Card reader is configured.
7 Azeti Nagios agent is running (required if inside the computer room)
8 Postfix does not listen or send mail locally.
9 No service listens on an IPv6 interface.
10 The nlmlhcnscanner account is properly configured.
